{"tid":2019725,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"累射19實彈 報告指無一違規","createTime":"2020-05-16T13:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T14:12:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8af2b0352cf9439b2ac59c0a67678bc6ed72bbc3","tid":2019725,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:15:50.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200516/INPFLSNKGCHAKJRG77LG3X62TE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200516%2FINPFLSNKGCHAKJRG77LG3X62TE%2F&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BSWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=f4ca9416\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200516%2FINPFLSNKGCHAKJRG77LG3X62TE%2F&h=aa2486c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200516/INPFLSNKGCHAKJRG77LG3X62TE/</a><br />\n<br />\n累射19實彈 報告指無一違規<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200516/large/1589561670_01d1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200516%2Flarge%2F1589561670_01d1.gif&h=8c7d25de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報告未有回應甚囂塵上的新屋嶺毆打及性侵指控。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年6月至今年2月間，警方共發射16,191枚催淚彈，有報道指有抗爭者過量吸入而死亡。監警會報告未有要求警方公開催淚彈成份，僅建議組專家委員會，探討催淚煙含量的可接受毒理水平，若無法界定何謂可接受水平，「警方可發放有關製造商、型號，以及任何已發展地區使用的相同型號催淚煙的資訊。」<br />\n<br />\n除了催淚彈外禍害，警暴追究無從也令民怨難平。監警會報告指，截至今年2月底，有關警員身份識別問題衍生的須滙報投。。。。。。。。。。。分別佔總數的 5.9%和 8.1%。而32宗須滙報投訴當中，有8宗涉及便衣警員，10宗涉及特別戰術小隊或防暴警員。<br />\n<br />\n監警會在報告中提及，俗稱「速龍小隊」的特別戰術小隊成員過往以戰術套裝沒有空間為由，沒有展示其職級或編號；有便衣警拒絕出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n監警會認為警隊管理層應視警員展示身份識別，為處理大型公眾活動的「最基本做法」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拒評新屋嶺性侵指控<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林卓廷轟報告嚴重扭曲歷史<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方於2019年8月11日使用位置偏遠的新屋嶺扣留中心拘留被捕者，事件引起公眾關注。監警會指新屋嶺沒有電。。。。。。。。。。。最受關注的毆打及性侵指控，報告則未有評論。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年2月29日，警方在反修例期間的12宗事件中，使用19發實彈，。。。。。。。。。。。報告總結警務人員於面臨致命襲擊時才發射實彈，保持克制。"},{"pid":"697e55c90095e03783428c8ae6cea1087f42a528","tid":2019725,"uid":34779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"其實用6個字就總括到成個report<br />\n你地冇做錯到"},{"pid":"7116dd8c64c589a7a5a422bf2332d8aa8bab14db","tid":2019725,"uid":281899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"697e55c90095e03783428c8ae6cea1087f42a528","tid":2019725,"uid":34779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"其實用6個字就總括到成個report<br />\n你地冇做錯到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:19:53.000Z","msg":"或者再短d, 4隻字<br />\n愛黨愛國"},{"pid":"ee71389bfd5e3c111a67e59900518187c0ea9a67","tid":2019725,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.plurk.com/5j6gZzXMLXkhdpkC68CU2l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.plurk.com%2F5j6gZzXMLXkhdpkC68CU2l.jpg&h=c8b06af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/05/04/HqiKB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F05%2F04%2FHqiKB2.jpg&h=89b9b1ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b3c128301f47d04d2a3cbb6dc95ba21fb5ae627","tid":2019725,"uid":197939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:12:16.000Z","msg":"推比民陣睇！想反國歌法嘅入尼！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2019775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2019775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}